    <item>
      <title>设置hostname，避免DHCP修改hostname</title>
      <link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/set_hostname/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/set_hostname/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;It can be annoying to see my hostname being modifed each time I connect to a different WIFI. It is because the hostname was never set.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;gt; scutil --get HostName 
HostName: not set 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So we just need to set the hostname:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;gt; sudo scutil --set HostName &amp;quot;new_hostname&amp;quot;  
Password:  
&amp;gt; scutil --get HostName              
new_hostname  
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description>
    </item>
